Package: shapeMageR
Title: Generation of Complex Geometry for Plotting
Version: 0.0.5
Authors@R: 
    person("Chun-Hui", "Gao", , "gaospecial@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1445-7939"))
Description: `shapeMageR` is implemented to deal with the shape generation for 
  plotting complex geometries in `ggVennDiagram`. It's named after "shape + 
  mage + R". All the related shape generation functions used in `ggVennDiagram`
  are transferred to the new `shapeMageR` package. 
